{"tid":1752402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府：愛比暴力強 與暴力割蓆","createTime":"2019-11-24T20:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T20:16:48.000Z","uid":117975,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"28b09fa1d3353726170aee37d7ba9d840467bc28","tid":1752402,"uid":117975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:07:40.000Z","msg":"政府依家一致既口吻就係叫大家習慣和平<br />\n個個政府人員同建制都講<br />\n話今日幾咁平靜 出黎投票既市民都係想咁樣<br />\n講到尾 都係一句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要大家同勇武割蓆</span></span><br />\n可惜 香港人唔係流<br />\n大家唔會忘記黑警同政府做過既野<br />\n612 721 831 101 新屋嶺 輪姦 浮屍 無血跳樓 二噁英 山埃 彥林 周梓樂 中大理大 仲有犧牲左既義士<br />\n數都數唔哂<br />\n區選只係場運動既一環 <br />\n黎緊又要重新上路<br />\n國際同本土抗爭都要繼續做<br />\n同埋 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span></span>呀 真係要做番<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9d29582babf7f5be56690c077b6e191600fb291d","tid":1752402,"uid":117975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:07:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f2ee853c76c739a548384571f59884d136ea3a0","tid":1752402,"uid":117975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:08:40.000Z","msg":"仲有 <br />\n唔好成日話政府冇招<br />\n黑警冇招<br />\n佢地一定仲有大把招"},{"pid":"387eda9b22df26d58afe462f67f51c5dcc67782f","tid":1752402,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:08:49.000Z","msg":"政府同黑警割未"},{"pid":"88b5fd6c23a0cab6b9296e886561b8fded0b67da","tid":1752402,"uid":117975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:08:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f612ae79e60ab244c15001055ae7d665cf1e223c","tid":1752402,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:09:06.000Z","msg":"同黑警割"},{"pid":"37c1ecf3930d1bdba1293b557a276a01b6200837","tid":1752402,"uid":59965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T20:09:15.000Z"